                    <article class="blog__item--2">
                        <div class="textBox">
                            <p>מגוון תוספים ומשפרי <br> מכלולים מבית FORTE</p>
                            <a href="https://forte.zoko-campaigns.com/" class="blog__btn" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><span>קרא עוד</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24.497" height="17.74" viewBox="0 0 24.497 17.74"><g data-name="Group 41007" transform="translate(23.497 16.326) rotate(180)"><path data-name="Path 25" d="M0,14.912,7.456,7.456,0,0" transform="translate(15.041)" fill="none" stroke="#3e87f7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"/><path data-name="Path 26" d="M21.445,0H0" transform="translate(0 7.456)" fill="none" stroke="#3e87f7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="2"/></g></svg></a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="imgBox"><img src="img/img_forte.jpg" alt="img"></div>
                    </article>
                </div>
                <div class="swiper-slide">
                    <article class="blog__item--3">
                        <div class="textBox">
                            <p>המעמיסים הטלסקופיים המובילים של המותג הבינלאומי מגני נחתו בישראל</p>
                            <a href="https://magni.ite-campaigns.com/" class="blog__btn" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><span>קרא עוד</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24.497" height="17.74" viewBox="0 0 24.497 17.74"><g data-name="Group 41007" transform="translate(23.497 16.326) rotate(180)"><path data-name="Path 25" d="M0,14.912,7.456,7.456,0,0" transform="translate(15.041)" fill="none" stroke="#3e87f7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"/><path data-name="Path 26" d="M21.445,0H0" transform="translate(0 7.456)" fill="none" stroke="#3e87f7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="2"/></g></svg></a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="imgBox"><img src="img/direction-3.webp" alt="img"></div>
                    </article>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>

